=== wand of fire ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed wand of fire
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed wand of fire
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed wand of fire
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a wand of fire
qty=1 unidentified -> an oak wand
qty=1 called=zap! -> a wand called zap!
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed wand of fires
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed wand of fires
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed wand of fires
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 wand of fires
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 oak wands
qty=3 called=zap! -> 3 wand called zap!s
